-- Costamagna Says Impregilo Can Become World Player, Sole Reports
-- B y   E l i s a   M a r t i n u z z i
-- 2012-06-03T10:12:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-03/costamagna-says-impregilo-can-become-world-player-sole-reports.html
Impregilo SpA (IPG)  can become a “strong
world player” in the construction industry with Salini
Costruttori SpA’s plan for the building company, Claudio
Costamagna, whom Salini proposed as chairman, said in an
interview with Il Sole 24 Ore.  Impregilo can become a “giant,” Costamagna, a former
chairman of European investment banking at Goldman Sachs Group
Inc., told the Italian newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisa Martinuzzi in Milan at 
